modified_SQL_query: UPDATE staging.FTP_Unpivot SET EQ(Dirty_space_Price, 0) WHERE AND(OR((AND(AND(AND(EQ(Level_4, 'Fixed Rate Mortgages'), COMPARE(instrument_set, ('mortgage', 'offset mortgage'))), EQ(external_counterparty_segment, 'households')), (OR(COMPARE(market_shock, '%SOT%'), COMPARE(market_shock, '%EVEatR%'))))), (AND(AND(EQ(Level_4, 'Fixed Rate Mortgage Savings'), EQ(instrument_set, 'mortgage savings')), (OR(COMPARE(market_shock, 'SOT%'), COMPARE(market_shock, 'EVEatR%')))))), (OR(COMPARE(Portfolio, '%OBV'), COMPARE(Portfolio, '%ABB'))))
